{"tid":1645804,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"畫左漫畫文宣解釋黨鐵惡行，有721，831","createTime":"2019-10-11T04:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T12:54:32.000Z","uid":284648,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"e1418876428a0bb39ea30db4cc44f9d0f5e8b6e3","tid":1645804,"uid":284648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:29:39.000Z","msg":"第一次出po 同P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日日聽到警謊同政府叫香港人同暴力割席<br />\n真心嬲<br />\n近日出tweet有位巴打問我可唔可以畫下港鐵，解釋俾小朋友聽點解要裝修，我覺得呢個idea幾好<br />\n雖然連登巴絲同我核爆都唔割<br />\n但唔上連登/唔係好了解既淺黃/藍,甚至小朋友<br />\n見黨鐵俾人裝修都未必會明白<br />\n藍既就話暴徒呀搞亂哂乜乜乜<br />\n聽完好心酸<br />\n<br />\n平時上街只係做到和理非，有時都嬲自己癈<br />\n希望平日畫多啲文宣幫到呢場運動<br />\n希望唔係同溫層既人<br />\n就算唔應同，都理解係咩事<br />\n雖然得幾頁但都畫左3日<br />\n有啲位未必太好，日後既文宣會再改進<br />\n鍾意既幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n印出黎，貼黨鐵門口又得<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n沒有暴徒！只有暴政！<br />\n香港人反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSGg03Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSGg03Z.png&h=4434fe2e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1rMkJhk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1rMkJhk.png&h=fac97f91&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/11/122550_7df0844e78cda9ed486b12b54557d430.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F11%2F122550_7df0844e78cda9ed486b12b54557d430.png&h=af8884b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/11/122551_a03c15b4322a2f55d34676d7c86186a5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F11%2F122551_a03c15b4322a2f55d34676d7c86186a5.png&h=5b6b427b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/11/122554_3f5694b832086151a7f5b7a48beefdde.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F11%2F122554_3f5694b832086151a7f5b7a48beefdde.png&h=2246e44d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/11/122557_cec6e493075e7643ddb0e818df463897.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F11%2F122557_cec6e493075e7643ddb0e818df463897.png&h=8e0ba631&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/11/122557_d9eaddb12a6adcabee45b85cb30a66ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F11%2F122557_d9eaddb12a6adcabee45b85cb30a66ab.png&h=3ecc4713&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1217e88b0a4cd2814aaeb3a0f80b6a166b64d156","tid":1645804,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:31:34.000Z","msg":"幫你推佢老母"},{"pid":"f8ed9a073d9c357d9670c17604f74b067cc5ab12","tid":1645804,"uid":286411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:32:48.000Z","msg":"推啊！好高汁"},{"pid":"3555a62c98695d9d1ad18198306359a3e701634a","tid":1645804,"uid":187339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:33:04.000Z","msg":"巴打勁"},{"pid":"fafbb2acd0e18270f6ecbe7c0aa8c363ef342614","tid":1645804,"uid":209158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:33:30.000Z","msg":"推 樓主畫得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3e8b45eafe075798bcafd934efed8636699a10","tid":1645804,"uid":34033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:35:31.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"7cd072411501c570fe917a6c894b7d1a32184cee","tid":1645804,"uid":42549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,